title: United Kingdom Imports of Sugars & Sugar Confectionery
description: Imports of Sugars & Sugar Confectionery in the United Kingdom increased to 131.74 GBP Million in September from 113.35 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports of Sugars & Sugar Confectionery in the United Kingdom averaged 84.79 GBP Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 139.63 GBP Million in November of 2008 and a record low of 46.33 GBP Million in December of 2001. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Sugars & Sugar Confectionery.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
